def f_gold(s: str) -> int:   # --- py stmt 2

    ans = 0   # --- py stmt 4
    chars = set()   # --- py stmt 5

            continue   # --- py stmt 8

            break   # --- py stmt 10

            chars.remove(s[i])   # --- py stmt 12
            i += 1   # --- py stmt 13

        ans = max(   # --- py stmt 16
          ans, i - j + 1
        )
    ans, i = ans * 2, i + 1   # --- py stmt 17
    return ans   # --- py stmt 18
